        <h3 style="-moz-osx-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #1a1a1a; font-family: 'SF Compact Display', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 1.375em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.16em; margin: 1em 0 0.625em 0;">
         <strong>
          Getting on Audio\xe2\x80\x99s Wavelength
          <br/>
         </strong>
        </h3>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         I have heard the future of audio, and no, this isn\xe2\x80\x99t another Clubhouse piece. I\xe2\x80\x99m talking about
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkE1uxCAMhU8zLKPwl4YFi256DUTAk6AQSMGZKj19mWRRybIlW0_P33MWYc7l1HuuSN7N4LmDTvBTIyBCIUeFYoLXdGAjl0IRr4WnoxxJqOZZADYbosZyANmPKQZnMeR0KfqeSbLoj8k78Jz5QQiQbFLuqTwMaqDAmVDy9rWHD5AcaHhBOXMCEvWCuNcH_3ywr1YxVISEec_-t3N5aysSNOsZ7SkbKZdSDh3tnHiBXL9R8vwQ_Tazrh5TRevWt4gUnTJOuYQ0t_O62A3idWjfmza3IwU8DSQ7RfA3GN75XKhmhgSl5eaNxZYKpaNgVDY2dYM0ck6VGAfFSXP2uanSv-kf_Qp-PA" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Podz
         </a>
         . Its solution, ten years in the making, has a legitimate shot at solving audio\xe2\x80\x99s biggest challenge.
        </p>
        <div class="captioned-image-container-static" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center;">
         <figure style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%;">
          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="image-wrapper" style="margin: 8px auto; mso-padding-alt: 1em 0 1.6em;" width="100%">
           <tbody>
            <tr>
             <td style="text-align: center;">
             </td>
             <td align="left" class="content" style="text-align: center;" width="550">
              <a class="image-link" href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxVkkuO5CAMhk9T7BLxTGDBotXSXCPi4aRQJZAGUj3Vp28qWYxGQrbBsn_LH85UWFJ-6T2Vit5mqq8ddITvskKtkNFRIE_BazJQyQRXyGvuiRQShTLNGWAzYdU1H4D2w67BmRpSPCswpgLdNVF2sBgMk1iMlFGHmZi5ItxarJiyl645fIDoQMMT8itFQKu-17qXG_u40T_tOB_7cthSjXv0Lm3tKWxmgeZnqO7-9q1NTTf6-XUF7GNJybf7vE57TkuGUsIT2nupAHuruCSoeIuIt0wz9nAPaPncARbWOsk7awzrOBuhU4LIznjLqIVxVJL3hfVmMz8pmu9yzdV6XLs4w3PIcoaEUw9kMB0DwB2XGHdKMto5akdm5CwFt5MS-C8VvN_jgoKmmBJMqCRMCDH0pHf8CeLxVQVLN463hf63FJR1TNWmHOLS0o-72WA9E22iqfntiKG-JojGruAvcPXif6KcFoiQ27_wk6mNOiGSUyIG3tCfoBpZRhSXg2KoKfvUquI_0V8CqcGT" style="border: none; display: block; height: auto; margin: 0; padding: 0; text-decoration: none; width: auto;" target="_blank">
