        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         \xe2\x80\xa6 wrote an in-depth report on the state of podcasting, called
         <em>
          <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkN1uwyAMhZ-m3DUKvyIXXOxmrxERcFPUBDJwOmVPPzedNMmyLdnmcL7gEeZSD7eVhuyVRjw2cBm-2wKIUNneoI4pOm6ElVoNLDoVudWWpTbeKsDq0-Kw7sC2fVpS8JhKPi_6Xmh2d1ZaYyBEHwcvvImT1kbdDIjhpoMG9db1e0yQAzh4Qj1KBra4O-LWLvLjIj4pPDc_XSgrtaLnA5Vev3pJaSsx-IZXCKUdDWG9pvyEhinP179llpzoBe-5sFxq-kPHu6CeoB9fqGW5qH6dRdf2qaEPj5cQqy4XnEqlV2j8uPsVlnNATkeq654THiNkPy0Q3xDwzfLEMs6QoRLjOHokgpxbJTi5J4ynaaIk-aCsGSQj5VjoKv-L_gK1rYp-" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
           Investing in the Podcast Ecosystem in 2019
          </a>
          .
         </em>
         It\xe2\x80\x99s a couple of years old now, but it\xe2\x80\x99s worth reading for a deeper dive into podcasting\xe2\x80\x99s history and landscape. In the report, a16z used data from Edison Research and Triton Digital to point out that, for the first time, more than half of Americans over the age of 12 had listened to a podcast. Edison and Triton\xe2\x80\x99s 2020
         <em>
          <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkdtqxCAQhp9mvUvwELPJhReFttDbHq6D0UkiazTVSZd9-7pZSkHmwM_MP3wajTDHdFNbzEjuYcDbBirANXtAhET2DGlwVrGWd0I2PbGqsayTHXF5mBLAqp1XmHYg2z56ZzS6GI4JSrkki9JGwiiAnq2R596Kc9vKsZlGfraCCgsPX71bB8GAgh9ItxiAeLUgbifxdOKv5V2v1xqsyzEkyKCTWWoT17uwVSYGhICl2Tcftc2l4pTTkqgo4XOB6i1MLjiE6tlpX93V6qv-qKuXY2f1_rd0sxNxquiMMt4xIaVsa1ab5gfk5RuliKeGrjOv8z5m1OZyP4MkFSKOMbkwF_my6BX8IRQoQ8nrXrxvAwQ9erAPXvjAfhAcZgiQynfYQWOBzVjXcCbbphA_-BSggvVN1_aCFGcby1T4N_0F82OaXA" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
