        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Today, time and ad money spent on podcasts is smaller but faster-growing than radio and TV.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         One of the main reasons for podcasts\xe2\x80\x99 growth has been that it\xe2\x80\x99s just easier and better to listen to audio on-the-go.AirPods, and AirPods Pro, have been a game-changer for the industry. Sales have nearly 6x\xe2\x80\x99ed since their first year on market in 2017, and if this growth keeps up, they will be Apple\xe2\x80\x99s third-largest product line by revenue next year.
        </p>
